Package: budgie-calendar-applet
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: Calendar Applet for the budgie-desktop
 Package that installs an Calendar applet for the 
 budgie-desktop. On hover the date is display.  On click
 the date and time together with the calendar is displayed.
